data.title: Buy Marvel’s Spider-Man 2 Collector's Edition – PS5
meta_keywords: Spider-Man. Spider-Man 2. Peter Parker. Miles Morales. Marvel’s New York. Kraven the Hunter. Lizard. Venom.
data.meta_description: Buy Marvel’s Spider-Man 2 Collector's Edition on PS5, available exclusively from PlayStation and swing, jump, and utilize the new Web Wings to travel across Marvel’s New York as Peter Parker and Miles Morales.
